<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/27512763-jacqueline-hendricks"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1395675443i/27512763._UY100_CR10,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
