        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2854621960" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9505606750495588804">“...the hands of none of us are clean if we bend not our energies to righting these great wrongs” ~W.E.B. Du Bois<br/><br/>Michelle Alexander’s critique of racism in America is thorough, honest, and illuminating. I would be skeptical of an “informed opinion” from anyone who has not read this book and come to terms with its indictments.</span>

          </span>
