<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18144031-redefining-realness"><img alt="Redefining Realness: My Path to Womanhood, Identity, Love &amp; So Much More" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1394420737l/18144031._SX98_.jpg" />
